Leave Request Approval System – Technical Specification
________________________________________
1. Objective
To implement a multi-level leave approval workflow in Google Sheets and Gmail using Google Apps Script that:
•	Supports leave requests initiated by Faculty or Chair.
•	Tracks approvals through Chair → Dean → Hospital Director (or direct to Director if Chair initiates).
•	Maintains a clear audit trail and logs.
•	Sends dynamic approval emails with editable “Hours Approved” and Yes/No buttons.
•	Minimizes unnecessary trigger activations.
•	Provides modular, maintainable, and scalable architecture.
________________________________________
2. Google Sheets Structure
All sheets are in one Google Spreadsheet for simplicity and efficiency.
2.1 LeaveRequest Sheet
Column	Description
A	Timestamp (form submission time)
B	Email Address of requestor
C	Department
D	Position (Faculty / Chair)
E	Type of Leave
F	From (Start Date)
G	To (End Date)
H	Additional Detail (optional text)
I	Total Hours Requested
J	Additional Information (optional)
K	Supporting Document Upload
L	Token Number (auto-generated, unique)
Notes: Columns M–U removed; all approvals are in separate sheets.
